room_title: Escape room "A Wrinkle of Wormhole" by That Escape Room in San Francisco
room_description: Brain Thomas is a 17-year-old prodigy who invented the time machine and opened a wormhole in the wrong way. His house contains both his room during 2017 & 2018. The wormhole gate is getting bigger, Brain freaked out and sent a bomb into the wormhole. It is going to explode soon. That'll change and mess up the timeline in the real world. You guys are the top graded scientists. You have to find the gate of the wormhole, deactivate the bomb, and get out of there.
